ath9k/mac80211: emit per-frame stream-0 EVM as radiotap LOCK_QUALITY

ar9003 carries per-(stream,pilot) EVM in the RX descriptor (evm0..4).
Average the valid (non-0x80) bytes -> for single-stream frames these are
exactly stream-0's pilots -> map to a 0-100 quality percent on the Realtek
3x|dB| scale, expose it via a new ieee80211_rx_status.evm field, and emit it
as the aggregate IEEE80211_RADIOTAP_LOCK_QUALITY (bit 7) so wfb-ng (which
already parses that field) reports EVM. Applies on top of the antnoise patch.

Regenerated by diff against the prepared backports-6.18.26 tree (real
ath9k_cmn_process_rssi signature, correct hunk offsets).

